<li class='cover' id='bookCover_218986'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/218986.The_Meadow"><img alt="The Meadow" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388184151l/218986._SX98_.jpg" />
